CHANGELOG.md-1766- - Improved OpenAI stream robustness for malformed trailing tool-call JSON in partial chunks.
CHANGELOG.md-1767- - Added built-in GLM-5 model support via z.ai and OpenRouter provider catalogs.
CHANGELOG.md-1768- 
CHANGELOG.md-1769- ### Breaking Changes
CHANGELOG.md-1770- 
CHANGELOG.md-1771- - `ContextUsage.tokens` and `ContextUsage.percent` are now `number | null`. After compaction, context token count is unknown until the next LLM response, so these fields return `null`. Extensions that read `ContextUsage` must handle the `null` case. Removed `usageTokens`, `trailingTokens`, and `lastUsageIndex` fields from `ContextUsage` (implementation details that should not have been public) ([#1382](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/1382) by [@ferologics](https://github.com/ferologics)... [truncated]
CHANGELOG.md-1772- - Git source parsing is now strict without `git:` prefix: only protocol URLs are treated as git (`https://`, `http://`, `ssh://`, `git://`). Shorthand sources like `github.com/org/repo` and `git@github.com:org/repo` now require the `git:` prefix. ([#1426](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/issues/1426))
CHANGELOG.md-1773- 
CHANGELOG.md-1774- ### Added
CHANGELOG.md-1775- 
CHANGELOG.md:1776: - Added extension event forwarding for message and tool execution lifecycles (`message_start`, `message_update`, `message_end`, `tool_execution_start`, `tool_execution_update`, `tool_execution_end`) ([#1375](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/1375) by [@sumeet](https://github.com/sumeet))
CHANGELOG.md-1777- - Added `terminal_input` extension event to intercept, consume, or transform raw terminal input before normal TUI handling.
CHANGELOG.md-1778- - Added `gpt-5.3-codex-spark` model definition for OpenAI and OpenAI Codex providers (research preview).
CHANGELOG.md-1779- 
CHANGELOG.md-1780- ### Changed
CHANGELOG.md-1781- 
CHANGELOG.md-1782- - Routed GitHub Copilot Claude 4.x models through Anthropic Messages API, with updated Copilot header handling for Claude model requests.
CHANGELOG.md-1783- 
CHANGELOG.md-1784- ### Fixed
CHANGELOG.md-1785- 
CHANGELOG.md-1786- - Fixed context usage percentage in footer showing stale pre-compaction values. After compaction the footer now shows `?/200k` until the next LLM response provides accurate usage ([#1382](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/1382) by [@ferologics](https://github.com/ferologics))
